This paper is about video summarization, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method uses reinforcement learning, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of subgoals and subtasks, which are common in multimedia computing (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
